## Task Summary: Place sotp binary at bin/sotp

**Track:** sotp-bin-placement-2026-03-15
**Task:** Install sotp to bin/ via bootstrap, replace cargo run in host wrappers and hooks
**Date:** 2026-03-15

### Changes

- bin/.gitkeep: New directory for sotp binary
- .gitignore: Exclude /bin/sotp from git
- Makefile.toml: build-sotp task, bootstrap Step 4/6, all host wrappers use bin/sotp
- .claude/settings.json: Hook fallback chain (SOTP_CLI_BINARY → bin/sotp → sotp → cargo run)
- .claude/agent-profiles.json: providers.codex.fast_model added
- .claude/commands/track/review.md: Model escalation strategy
- scripts/*: Updated test expectations

### Why

Replace cargo run overhead (~hundreds of ms per invocation) with pre-built bin/sotp. Hook fallback chain ensures fresh clones still work via cargo run. Bootstrap automatically builds and installs the binary.
